high_descs: Turn around and go near the countertop.
Take the knife from the table.
Turn around and go to the bedroom.
There is a lettuce on the bed.
Cut the cabbage into pieces using the knife on the bed.
Then put the knife on the bed.
Turn and go near the bed.
Take the piece of lettuce from the bed.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the piece of lettuce into the refrigerator.
Then take it out and go near the microwave.
Put the lettuce into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the piece of lettuce into the microwave oven.

high_descs: Turn right and exit the room through the doorway ahead, turn right and go forward until reaching the kitchen area on the left, then approach the microwave on the countertop in the corner.
Pick up the knife from the counter next to the microwave.
Exit the kitchen area and turn left in the large room to enter the bedroom ahead, then head towards the lettuce bed.
Slice the lettuce on the bed.
Look to the bottle on the bed.
Place the knife next to the bed.
Turn back to the bed.
Pick up the lettuce.
Return to the kitchen area and head to the fridge in the corner.
Put the lettuce in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn right and head to the microwave.
Put the lettuce in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cut up some lettuce, cool a piece of Lettuce in a fridge and place it in a Microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, leave the room through an entrance in the upper right, head right alongside the wall on your left and then left to a kitchen corner, where you find a microwave on the countertop.
Pick up the knife from next to the microwave.
Turn around, walk to the middle of the hall, then go left, enter a room and walk to the lettuce from a position right near a nightstand.
Cut the lettuce on the bed with the knife.
Take a step right so you are right next to the bed.
Drop the knife on the bed.
Take a step back left so you are in front of the bed.
Pick up the lettuce slice from the bed.
Head back to the kitchen corner and approach the fridge there.
Place the lettuce slice in the fridge, let it cool there for a while, then take it out.
Go right from there to the microwave.
Put the lettuce slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Get the cooled lettuce slice in the microwave
